data.description: Nestled on 17.16 acres of pure tranquility, this exceptional property is a true gem waiting to be discovered. The large, distinctive main house boasts spacious rooms, a sunroom, an office, and ample porch space, inviting you to savor the beauty of your surroundings.  Additionally there are two 3-car garages, one featuring a partially finished loft, offering versatility and additional potential. A charming barn, a picturesque pond, approximately 12 fully fenced acres, and an in-ground pool all enhance the allure of this unique property.  Indulge in outdoor living on the covered deck with a fireplace, providing the perfect spot to unwind and entertain. The land, predominantly level, offers a canvas for your dreams. As you drive down the long driveway, a secluded personal oasis unfolds, shielding you from the world and offering the utmost privacy.  While this property requires a bit of TLC to reach its full potential, it is undeniably something special. The land opens up possibilities for horses, a mini-farm, or any dream you envision. Don't miss the chance to own this rare find – a captivating retreat that promises a lifestyle of serenity, space, and endless possibilities!
